						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,2354738)"></a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203958" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;" >Decibelles</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1439172734 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">10 Aug 2015 02:12</span>
