<p>I had to actually check on the Blade / Sword thing myself, but it is Sword.</p>
<p>The Swords (all seven of them) serve as major generals of the Daevite army, yes. The First is of course the most important - their cult is not the only one in the legions (Moloch is a popular one, as are dead Swords, and plenty of minor gods) Some Swords might not get cults, if they aren't good enough, and popularity waxes and wanes.</p>
<p>Then sometimes a Sword of lower rank takes the top spot by force.</p>

