				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203958" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;" >Decibelles</a></span> <span class="odate time_1439187085 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">10 Aug 2015 06:11</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2354809">
									

<p>Ana is commonly shorthand for Anorexia Nervosa. The skip referenced is <a href="/scp-1052">SCP-1052</a>, which utilizes anorexia for the story hook, which is heavily referenced here with all of its symptoms. I mean, it's not a subtle thing.</p>

