			<div class="content" id="post-content-2354817">
									

<p>I've read that skip before, and I got the connection, but it seemed like typical Djoric stuff, wherein there's <em>way</em> more to a simple skip than is seen by we readers. It didn't seem like he was saying anything the article wasn't.</p>

