			<div class="content" id="post-content-2354819">
									

<p>Hey Rademacher, please tone down the harshness. It's coming off as excessive; you shouldn't need to use phrases like &quot;Just don't.&quot; and &quot;crappy&quot;.</p>
<p>Additionally, in regards to this statement:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>I would be ashamed to submit this as a draft, let alone a polished piece.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This is wholly unnecessary. Please be more conscientious when reviewing work. If you find that doing so is making you frustrated, step away from the review and do something else. Additionally, if you're upset with someone's behavior, inform a staff member so they can address it accordingly.</p>

